Package: ffcast
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: libav-tools|ffmpeg|recordmydesktop, x11-utils
Description: Screen recording wrapper for Unix cli screencast utilities
 ffcast helps the user interactively select a screen region and hands over the
 geometry to an external command, such as ffmpeg, for screen recording.
